Items.name: Bacan Canvas Black Casual Shoes For Men
Items.description: Let's take a moment to honor an icon. Is it the gravity-defying B-ball legend from the '80s? Or perhaps the status shoe that adorned the feet of rappers? Both, in fact. The adidas Forum shoes have dominated the hardwood and the streets, and they're back in a mid top version to take your moves to the next level. Slip into the unmistakable style, now in luxurious coated leather, and flaunt that pure class.
